code: /* eslint-disable no-console */import axios from"axios";var interceptorEnabled=false;if(process.env.NODE_ENV!=="production"){interceptorEnabled=true;}var axiosInstance=axios.create({baseURL:"https://flats9.herokuapp.com"});axiosInstance.interceptors.request.use(function(request){if(interceptorEnabled){console.log("Request: ".concat(request.method," ").concat(request.baseURL).concat(request.url));}return request;});axiosInstance.interceptors.response.use(function(response){if(interceptorEnabled){console.log("Response Status: ",response.status);console.log("Response Summary: ",response.data.summary);console.log("Response Content: ",response.data.data);}return response;},function(error){console.log("Error",error);return error;});export default axiosInstance;
